    "# vis-bridge\n\nPkg: `com.blockether/vis-bridge`. Src: `extensions/common/vis-bridge/`.\n\nSingle alias: `bridge/`.\n\n## v1 extraction\n\n```clojure\n(bridge/clojure-lsp-status)\n(bridge/extract-markdown \"docs/src/SUMMARY.md\")\n(bridge/extract-clojure {:project-root \".\"})\n```\n\nBridge v1 uses CommonMark for Markdown section trees and external `clojure-lsp dump` for Clojure semantic analysis. Tree-sitter is deliberately not a v1 dependency.\n"}}}}
